{"tid":1917140,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020選舉] 若論「顧全大局」","createTime":"2020-03-09T10:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T12:42:13.000Z","uid":49781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae919853d878c4219d616675cd382ccb8164679","tid":1917140,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:12:34.000Z","msg":"假設民主派選舉名單今年由泛民、本土、素人互相協調<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<br />\n直選組別嘅名單應該俾<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">本土 + 素人</span></strong>佔七成，<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">泛民</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">新人</span></strong>(走左膠)佔其餘三成，<br />\n<br />\n功能組別就俾其餘<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>泛民</strong></span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黃色經濟圈老闆</strong></span>去攻，<br />\n<br />\n咁樣會唔會同時Cover到「支持泛民、支持攻功能組別」同「反對攻功能組別」兩邊人嘅光譜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c82749266acc228421ca67f6bb0115b0507fe28","tid":1917140,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n1/5"},{"pid":"c694badc348187c400ef8b5a7123f0863564b52f","tid":1917140,"uid":272726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:35:05.000Z","msg":"仲有預計贏幾多席，就派幾多張名單去選。<br />\n<br />\n好處有：<br />\n1. 減少內鬥；<br />\n2. 承上，少咗內鬥就唔會搶走輿論；<br />\n3. 節省資源；<br />\n4. 承上，善用資源更集中投入至其他抗爭路線。<br />\n<br />\n選舉從來唔係主線，個個當哂主線去打去鬥，好容易釀成災難，例如住限內鬥、假希望破碎、其他戰線唔夠資源唔夠人等等。<br />\n<br />\n不過，前提係班泛民老屎忽肯放手，然後endorse班本土素人。<br />\n但而家選前吹風已經吹撚咗N張名單出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740a5bba2543e9e53aeb9b56fed3c8c57d27fd20","tid":1917140,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n2/5"},{"pid":"0db1c5dfbfa1ec0b98e9f71304cee0eef873d5e3","tid":1917140,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n3/5"},{"pid":"8a29a4875646dd51c51732566e468f748e22f3c4","tid":1917140,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:42:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n4/5"}]}